    "Regarding workplace and road safety, the use of mobile toilets at companies received a low score of 0.05 (Q14).",
    "Overtaking bans on highways scored only 0.14 (Q24).",
    "Aids in vehicles were assigned a score of 0.72, indicating a general agreement about their contribution to road safety (Q29).",
    "Furthermore, respondents found that a standalone air conditioner contributes to road safety (Q18, score: 0.89).",
    "A score of 0.91 was reported for the feeling that space on the roads has decreased, indicating a universal observation (Q22)."
